ChangeList.Description: Added the [check in](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-checkin?view=graph-rest-v1.0) and [check out](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-checkin?view=graph-rest-v1.0) actions on the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-v1.0) resource.

Added the **expirationDateTime**, **password**, and **message** properties on the [createLink](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-createlink?view=graph-rest-1.0) action on a [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **preventsDownload** property on the [sharingLink](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/sharinglink?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **permission** property on the [sharedDriveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/shareddriveitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **expirationDateTime**, **hasPassword**, and **grantedToIdentities** properties on the [permission](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/permission?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **expirationDateTime**, and **password** properties on the [invite](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-invite?view=graph-rest-1.0) action on a [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added **image** and **video** properties on the [remoteItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/remoteitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource. These properties allow you to retrieve media type thumbnails when combined with an expand function.
Added the **grant** action to the [permission](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/permission?view=graph-rest-1.0) entity.
Added the **following** navigation property to the [drive](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/drive?view=graph-rest-v1.0) entity.
Added the [follow](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-follow?view=graph-rest-v1.0) action on [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-v1.0).

Added the [unfollow](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-unfollow?view=graph-rest-v1.0) action on [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-v1.0).

Added the [pendingOperations](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/pendingOperations?view=graph-rest-beta) and [pendingContentUpdate](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/pendingContentUpdate?view=graph-rest-beta) resources. The **pendingOperations** resource applies to the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveItem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [restore](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-restore?view=graph-rest-beta) action to the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveItem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **orientation** property to the [photo](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/photo?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **sha256Hash** property to the [hashes](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/hashes?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [unfollow](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-unfollow?view=graph-rest-beta) action on [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-beta)
Added the **expirationDatetime** and **password** properties to the [createLink](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-createlink?view=graph-rest-beta) action.
Added the [bundle](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/bundle?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type
Added the [album](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/album?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type
Added the **bundles** navigation property to the [drive](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/drive?view=graph-rest-beta) entity
Added the **bundle** property to the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-beta) entity
Added the **grant** action to the [permission](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/permission?view=graph-rest-beta) entity
Added the **analytics** property to the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the **analytics** property to the [site](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/site?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the **analytics** property to the [listItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/listitem?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the **getActivitiesByInterval** function on the [driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/driveitem?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the **getActivitiesByInterval** function on the [site](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/site?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the **getActivitiesByInterval** function on the [listItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/listitem?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the [itemAnalytics](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/itemanalytics?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the [itemActivityStat](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/itemactivity?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the [itemActionStat](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/itemactionstat?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type.
Added the [accessAction](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessaction?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type.
Added the [incompleteData](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/incompletedata?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type.
Added the **access** property to the [itemActivity](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/itemactivity?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type.
Added the **location** property to the [itemActivity](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/itemactivity?view=graph-rest-beta) complex type.
